---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Roof Repairs Centenary Heights | Storm & Hail Damage"
  description="Roof repairs in Centenary Heights, Toowoomba — leak repairs, ridge capping, flashings, hail & wind damage on this elevated, storm-exposed suburb. QBCC-licensed. Free quote."
  canonical="https://toowoombaroofrepairs.com.au/centenary-heights/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Centenary Heights &middot; elevated &amp; storm-exposed</span>
      <h1>Roof repairs in <span class="accent">Centenary Heights</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Centenary Heights sits high and exposed on the Toowoomba range &mdash;
        which is exactly why its roofs take more wind and hail punishment than
        most. Lifted ridge capping, peeled flashings, cracked tiles and storm
        leaks are the bread-and-butter repairs here. We make storm-hit roofs safe
        fast and handle the insurance claim. QBCC-licensed.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Centenary Heights</span>
      <h2>Roofing on Toowoomba&rsquo;s exposed high ground.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Elevation means wind &mdash; and wind lifts roofs.</h3>
        <p>
          Being one of the more elevated suburbs, Centenary Heights gets the full
          force of the storm gusts that sweep across the range. Wind is what
          lifts ridge and hip capping, peels back flashings, and finds the weak
          fixing on a metal roof &mdash; so wind-lift damage is the single most
          common repair we do up here. The fix is to re-bed and flexible-repoint
          the capping and re-fix to <strong>AS 1170.2</strong> wind ratings so it
          holds next time, not just looks tidy today.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Hail on top of the wind.</h3>
        <p>
          The same elevated, exposed position that brings the wind also puts
          Centenary Heights in the path of the Darling Downs hail. Hail cracks
          tiles and bruises metal sheets, and the combination of hail and high
          wind in a single supercell is what turns a small problem into a roomful
          of water damage. Storm and hail damage is generally an insurance matter
          &mdash; we make the roof safe first and deal with your assessor; see
          <a href="/services/storm-hail-damage/">storm &amp; hail damage</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Flashings are the weak point on an exposed roof.</h3>
        <p>
          On a windy, exposed site the flashings around chimneys, skylights,
          vents and wall abutments take a hammering, and they&rsquo;re where
          chronic leaks start. We reseal or replace flashings properly rather
          than running a bead of silicone over a failing one &mdash; see our
          <a href="/services/roof-repairs/">roof repairs</a> page. If the whole
          roof is tired and exposed, a <a href="/services/metal-roofing/">Colorbond
          reroof</a> with proper wind-rated fixing is often the more durable
          long-term answer.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Centenary Heights jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Re-bed and re-fix storm-lifted ridge capping after a wind event</li>
          <li>Reseal or replace failed flashings around penetrations and abutments</li>
          <li>Hail-damage make-safe and insurance-claim repair</li>
          <li>Leak repair from wind-driven rain getting under capping or flashings ($450&ndash;$1,200)</li>
          <li>Colorbond reroof with full wind-rated fixing for an exposed home ($18K&ndash;$35K)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/rangeville/">Rangeville</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/highfields/">Highfields</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/wilsonton/">Wilsonton</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/glenvale/">Glenvale</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/toowoomba-region/">All Toowoomba Region</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Centenary Heights roof quote.</h2>
        <p>Storm-lifted capping, leaks or hail damage on an exposed home &mdash; we&rsquo;ll get up there and give you an honest price.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
